WEBVTT

00:00:00.480 --> 00:00:03.510
Good evening, family. Praise the Lord.

00:00:03.520 --> 00:00:05.829
Thank you for joining me today. Well, I

00:00:05.839 --> 00:00:07.829
have some things on my heart and I

00:00:07.839 --> 00:00:09.430
appreciate every single one of you

00:00:09.440 --> 00:00:12.390
coming out so late this evening. But as

00:00:12.400 --> 00:00:14.070
I've been praying this afternoon,

00:00:14.080 --> 00:00:16.950
driving around like I normally do,

00:00:16.960 --> 00:00:19.830
the Lord had some things to say

00:00:19.840 --> 00:00:23.189
concerning what's coming. And so, I was just

00:00:23.199 --> 00:00:26.310
interceding for the nations, like

00:00:26.320 --> 00:00:30.630
my wife and I do, and our kids.

00:00:30.640 --> 00:00:33.190
He opened my eyes and he said, "I want

00:00:33.200 --> 00:00:34.709
to show you some things that are coming.

00:00:34.719 --> 00:00:36.950
It's very

00:00:36.950 --> 00:00:36.960
serious."And

00:00:36.960 --> 00:00:39.590
so, I'm going to go into that for

00:00:39.600 --> 00:00:42.229
you, but first, I want to show you what

00:00:42.239 --> 00:00:45.670
we stopped. I believe in prayer. You

00:00:45.680 --> 00:00:47.990
know, it's amazing when we come

00:00:48.000 --> 00:00:50.630
together as a body; many hands make

00:00:50.640 --> 00:00:53.910
light work. And so, I want to play this

00:00:53.920 --> 00:00:56.549
video for you because I believe this

00:00:56.559 --> 00:01:00.150
video is a result of our prayer

00:01:00.160 --> 00:01:01.910
group here. You know, I know there's

00:01:01.920 --> 00:01:03.750
other people praying, folks, but I

00:01:03.760 --> 00:01:07.910
believe we have a great push

00:01:07.920 --> 00:01:10.950
as a body with as many as assembled here

00:01:10.960 --> 00:01:13.190
together. I mean, there's thousands. I

00:01:13.200 --> 00:01:15.429
mean, the last video we had over 50,000

00:01:15.439 --> 00:01:17.429
people praying within that two-hour

00:01:17.439 --> 00:01:21.190
period. We had almost 300

00:01:21.200 --> 00:01:23.990
salvations, and we give all the glory

00:01:24.000 --> 00:01:26.390
to God with that. We started a new

00:01:26.400 --> 00:01:29.270
week now, but in last week, we had over

00:01:29.280 --> 00:01:31.670
1,500 people get born again on this

00:01:31.680 --> 00:01:34.069
channel, and so it made me really

00:01:34.079 --> 00:01:37.190
excited. I told Braden, I said, "We

00:01:37.200 --> 00:01:39.990
are making... you know, like when

00:01:40.000 --> 00:01:41.670
you see those ice breakers going through

00:01:41.680 --> 00:01:43.670
there, we're busting the ice."And so,

00:01:43.680 --> 00:01:45.670
nobody lost their life. And in the

00:01:45.680 --> 00:01:48.550
article, when you read about that,

00:01:48.560 --> 00:01:51.830
they lit the fuse underneath that news

00:01:51.840 --> 00:01:54.950
vehicle and it didn't go off.

00:01:54.960 --> 00:01:58.149
It didn't go off. So, it's faulty. So,

00:01:58.159 --> 00:02:00.709
that's the hand of God. We see the hand

00:02:00.719 --> 00:02:03.350
of God in motion protecting our people

00:02:03.360 --> 00:02:05.429
even whenever they may not even realize

00:02:05.439 --> 00:02:07.749
that they're being protected. Angels

00:02:07.759 --> 00:02:10.070
unaware. And I just want to

00:02:10.080 --> 00:02:12.150
give all the glory to

00:02:12.160 --> 00:02:13.750
God tonight. It's something to

00:02:13.760 --> 00:02:15.910
rejoice over because we can see prayers

00:02:15.920 --> 00:02:19.430
working. So, another thing,

00:02:19.440 --> 00:02:21.030
this is what the Lord was showing me

00:02:21.040 --> 00:02:22.470
because I just wanted to recap and show

00:02:22.480 --> 00:02:24.470
you that, because there were some people

00:02:24.480 --> 00:02:27.589
that sent that to me and I was just

00:02:27.599 --> 00:02:29.510
excited about it. I just believe that

00:02:29.520 --> 00:02:31.350
was in Utah. So, and we know there's

00:02:31.360 --> 00:02:33.750
much, much more. We know by the spirit of

00:02:33.760 --> 00:02:35.910
God that there's much, much more people

00:02:35.920 --> 00:02:38.470
just like this that we're going to pray

00:02:38.480 --> 00:02:41.509
that their plans

00:02:41.519 --> 00:02:44.470
would be foiled, that the darkness would

00:02:44.480 --> 00:02:47.910
be exposed, that the light would shine,

00:02:47.920 --> 00:02:50.309
and that God would get the glory for

00:02:50.319 --> 00:02:52.790
protecting the people in these last days.

00:02:52.800 --> 00:02:55.830
I told you, if you are in that area,

00:02:55.840 --> 00:02:57.990
if you're in these areas, that you go

00:02:58.000 --> 00:03:00.150
around pleading the blood of Jesus,

00:03:00.160 --> 00:03:01.509
applying the blood, going down the

00:03:01.519 --> 00:03:02.869
streets, praying protection

00:03:02.879 --> 00:03:05.830
over your city. And I believe as we do

00:03:05.840 --> 00:03:09.270
this as a body, according to Ephesians,

00:03:09.280 --> 00:03:11.509
that we are seated with him in

00:03:11.519 --> 00:03:12.949
the heavenlies far above all

00:03:12.959 --> 00:03:15.110
principalities and powers. I believe

00:03:15.120 --> 00:03:17.750
that if we take our place of authority,

00:03:17.760 --> 00:03:19.589
we will stop more and more

00:03:19.599 --> 00:03:22.229
of things like this in the days ahead.

00:03:22.239 --> 00:03:24.550
So, it's exciting because the Lord told

00:03:24.560 --> 00:03:28.229
me, "You must pray for Chicago."Chicago is

00:03:28.229 --> 00:03:28.239
a hotspot

00:03:28.239 --> 00:03:30.390
right now.

00:03:30.400 --> 00:03:33.270
Chicago, Boston,

00:03:33.280 --> 00:03:35.910
Philadelphia, New York City, and

00:03:35.920 --> 00:03:38.070
Washington, D.C. Not saying that these

00:03:38.080 --> 00:03:41.430
other places are not a hotspot, but

00:03:41.440 --> 00:03:43.509
there's strategic things that the Lord

00:03:43.519 --> 00:03:45.990
showed me about these five cities that

00:03:46.000 --> 00:03:50.550
I cannot go into publicly. It

00:03:50.560 --> 00:03:52.710
just... yeah, I'm just never

00:03:52.720 --> 00:03:55.589
going to do that right now. So, I

00:03:55.599 --> 00:03:58.229
just want you to be really... have your

00:03:58.239 --> 00:04:00.630
eyes open if you live in those areas and

00:04:00.640 --> 00:04:02.550
praying over your city on a day-to-day

00:04:02.560 --> 00:04:05.990
basis. And so, we know that the

00:04:06.000 --> 00:04:07.830
dark is getting darker and the light is

00:04:07.840 --> 00:04:10.630
getting lighter. Now, this is what I saw

00:04:10.640 --> 00:04:12.869
today and I'm going to get into it and

00:04:12.879 --> 00:04:14.630
I'll go over the things that the Lord

00:04:14.640 --> 00:04:16.150
showed me. And like I said, I'll try to

00:04:16.160 --> 00:04:18.310
keep this as short as possible, but I

00:04:18.320 --> 00:04:20.710
want you to hear this lady that's about

00:04:20.720 --> 00:04:24.150
to speak over... I believe it's the...

00:04:24.160 --> 00:04:25.909
it's not the United Nations. I don't

00:04:25.919 --> 00:04:28.469
know what this is, but she spoke and

00:04:28.479 --> 00:04:32.629
she's saying exactly what we got in

00:04:32.639 --> 00:04:34.150
prayer.

00:04:34.639 --> 00:04:35.430
State of the Union.

00:04:35.440 --> 00:04:37.030
The State of the Union. So, this is a

00:04:37.040 --> 00:04:39.510
State of the Union...

00:04:39.520 --> 00:04:39.990
Yeah,

00:04:40.000 --> 00:04:42.629
yeah. So, go ahead and play this lady.

00:04:42.639 --> 00:04:44.950
And she's, I guess, some kind of boss or

00:04:44.960 --> 00:04:46.629
something. I don't know who she is, but

00:04:46.639 --> 00:04:49.110
she says what we're praying

00:04:49.120 --> 00:04:50.390
about and what the Lord told us they

00:04:50.400 --> 00:04:52.390
were going to say. So, I want you to hear

00:04:52.400 --> 00:04:53.830
part of this. There was part of it that

00:04:53.840 --> 00:04:57.590
was

00:04:57.600 --> 00:05:00.230
alarming. Needless to say, it

00:05:00.240 --> 00:05:02.230
was pretty bad. But just play this. Can

00:05:02.240 --> 00:05:07.510
you play some of it? Son.

00:05:07.520 --> 00:05:09.909
Honorable members.

00:05:09.919 --> 00:05:12.790
What is happening in Gaza

00:05:12.800 --> 00:05:17.110
has shaken the conscience of the world.

00:05:17.120 --> 00:05:22.070
People killed while begging for food.

00:05:22.080 --> 00:05:25.909
Mothers holding lifeless babies.

00:05:25.919 --> 00:05:29.990
These images are simply catastrophic.

00:05:30.000 --> 00:05:33.110
So, I want to start with a very clear

00:05:33.120 --> 00:05:35.189
message:

00:05:35.199 --> 00:05:39.350
man-made famine can never be a weapon of

00:05:39.360 --> 00:05:42.710
war. For the sake of the children, for

00:05:42.720 --> 00:05:58.950
the sake of humanity, this must stop.

00:05:58.960 --> 00:06:01.749
This is also part of a more systematic

00:06:01.759 --> 00:06:04.950
shift in the last month that is simply

00:06:04.960 --> 00:06:06.870
unacceptable.

00:06:06.880 --> 00:06:09.029
We have seen the financial suffocation

00:06:09.039 --> 00:06:11.749
of the Palestinian Authority.

00:06:11.759 --> 00:06:13.749
The plans for settlement project in the

00:06:13.759 --> 00:06:17.749
so-called E1 area which would easily cut

00:06:17.759 --> 00:06:20.629
off the occupied West Bank from East

00:06:20.639 --> 00:06:23.430
Jerusalem, the actions and statements by

00:06:23.440 --> 00:06:25.270
the most extremist ministers of the

00:06:25.280 --> 00:06:27.990
Israeli government which incite

00:06:28.000 --> 00:06:31.430
violence. All of this points to a clear

00:06:31.440 --> 00:06:34.629
attempt to undermine the two-state

00:06:34.639 --> 00:06:37.990
solution, to undermine the vision of a

00:06:38.000 --> 00:06:41.270
viable Palestinian state. And we must

00:06:41.280 --> 00:06:53.270
not let this happen.

00:06:53.280 --> 00:06:55.270
And honorable members, it truly pains me

00:06:55.280 --> 00:06:57.909
to say these words. And I know that for

00:06:57.919 --> 00:07:01.430
many citizens, Europe's inability to

00:07:01.440 --> 00:07:05.510
agree on a common way forward is equally

00:07:05.520 --> 00:07:07.110
painful.

00:07:07.120 --> 00:07:09.510
They are asking how much worse things

00:07:09.520 --> 00:07:12.790
must get before there is unity in

00:07:12.800 --> 00:07:16.629
response. I understand

00:07:16.639 --> 00:07:18.550
because what is happening in Gaza is

00:07:18.560 --> 00:07:20.469
unacceptable

00:07:20.479 --> 00:07:22.870
and because Europe must lead the way,

00:07:22.880 --> 00:07:26.469
just as it has done before.

00:07:26.479 --> 00:07:28.390
Our financial support and humanitarian

00:07:28.400 --> 00:07:31.110
aid far outweigh that of any other

00:07:31.120 --> 00:07:33.830
partner. Our commitment to a viable

00:07:33.840 --> 00:07:35.990
Palestinian Authority is keeping the

00:07:36.000 --> 00:07:39.510
two-state solution alive and we must

00:07:39.520 --> 00:07:43.510
urge others to urgently step up, both

00:07:43.520 --> 00:07:46.550
in the region and beyond.

00:07:46.560 --> 00:07:52.629
But of course, Europe needs to do more.

00:07:52.639 --> 00:07:59.990
Many,

00:08:00.000 --> 00:08:02.150
many member states have moved ahead on

00:08:02.160 --> 00:08:06.469
their own. On our side, we proposed to

00:08:06.479 --> 00:08:09.990
suspend parts of our Horizon funding,

00:08:10.000 --> 00:08:13.749
but this is stuck without a majority.

00:08:13.759 --> 00:08:17.589
We must overcome this. We cannot afford

00:08:17.599 --> 00:08:19.589
to be paralyzed.

00:08:19.599 --> 00:08:22.309
And this is why I will propose a package

00:08:22.319 --> 00:08:26.950
of measures to carve out a way forward.

00:08:26.960 --> 00:08:28.950
First,

00:08:28.960 --> 00:08:32.230
the Commission will do all that it can

00:08:32.240 --> 00:08:35.190
do on its own.

00:08:35.200 --> 00:08:37.990
We will put our bilateral support to

00:08:38.000 --> 00:08:40.550
Israel on hold.

00:08:40.560 --> 00:08:44.710
We will stop all payments in these areas

00:08:44.720 --> 00:08:47.750
without affecting our work with Israeli

00:08:47.760 --> 00:08:51.670
civil society or

00:08:51.670 --> 00:08:51.680
Yad

00:08:51.680 --> 00:08:53.190
Vashem.

00:08:53.200 --> 00:08:56.230
We will make two further proposals to

00:08:56.240 --> 00:08:58.070
the council.

00:08:58.080 --> 00:09:00.949
We will propose sanctions on the

00:09:00.959 --> 00:09:03.430
extremist ministers and on violent

00:09:03.440 --> 00:09:18.230
settlers,

00:09:18.240 --> 00:09:20.470
and we will also propose a partial

00:09:20.480 --> 00:09:23.110
suspension of the Association Agreement

00:09:23.120 --> 00:09:37.030
on trade-related matters.

00:09:37.040 --> 00:09:41.110
I am aware it will be difficult to find

00:09:41.120 --> 00:09:42.790
majorities

00:09:42.800 --> 00:09:46.230
and I know that any action will be too

00:09:46.240 --> 00:09:51.190
much for one and too little for others.

00:09:51.200 --> 00:09:53.750
But we must all take our own

00:09:53.760 --> 00:09:55.430
responsibility:

00:09:55.440 --> 00:09:56.949
Parliament,

00:09:56.959 --> 00:10:00.790
council, Commission.

00:10:00.800 --> 00:10:03.110
My third point:

00:10:03.120 --> 00:10:05.590
we will set up a Palestine donor group

00:10:05.600 --> 00:10:08.550
next month, including a dedicated

00:10:08.560 --> 00:10:14.630
instrument for Gaza reconstruction.

00:10:14.640 --> 00:10:21.430
This...

00:10:21.440 --> 00:10:23.269
you basically get the gist of what's

00:10:23.279 --> 00:10:25.430
going on. I don't need to keep

00:10:25.440 --> 00:10:27.269
rehearsing everything that the woman's

00:10:27.279 --> 00:10:29.269
saying and what they want to do. But

00:10:29.279 --> 00:10:32.310
it's what the Lord told us was coming.

00:10:32.320 --> 00:10:34.470
Everything that she's saying in front of

00:10:34.480 --> 00:10:36.230
all those people, and they're applauding,

00:10:36.240 --> 00:10:38.389
is a two-state solution. They're

00:10:38.399 --> 00:10:41.030
coming up with a plan for a two-state

00:10:41.040 --> 00:10:43.829
solution for the week... I believe that

00:10:43.839 --> 00:10:46.069
we'll see it unfolding in the days ahead

00:10:46.079 --> 00:10:49.509
even more, for the week of the 21st,

00:10:49.519 --> 00:10:53.030
23rd, the main week of the UN.

00:10:53.040 --> 00:10:55.030
And this is what they voted on on the

00:10:55.040 --> 00:10:58.310
11th for a two-state solution to

00:10:58.320 --> 00:11:00.389
divide the land of Israel, recognizing

00:11:00.399 --> 00:11:03.829
Palestine as a state. And so, we see the

00:11:03.839 --> 00:11:06.550
things that the Lord told us were coming

00:11:06.560 --> 00:11:10.470
in prayer on this channel months ago

00:11:10.480 --> 00:11:12.550
and it's happening. And that's why the

00:11:12.560 --> 00:11:15.750
Lord told us, he said, "September will be a

00:11:15.760 --> 00:11:19.590
month to remember, a great

00:11:19.590 --> 00:11:19.600
acceleration."Watch

00:11:19.600 --> 00:11:22.069
the fig tree, which is Israel.

00:11:22.079 --> 00:11:24.150
Watch these things in the days ahead.

00:11:24.160 --> 00:11:26.230
And he warned us, and this

00:11:26.240 --> 00:11:29.110
is a major speech going forth in front

00:11:29.120 --> 00:11:31.590
of all these people about how to defund

00:11:31.600 --> 00:11:33.350
it, how to defund Israel, not giving

00:11:33.360 --> 00:11:35.350
them, doing all these things, and

00:11:35.360 --> 00:11:38.310
causing—talking

00:11:38.320 --> 00:11:40.069
about a two-state solution.

00:11:40.079 --> 00:11:43.269
Well, in prayer today, as I was driving

00:11:43.279 --> 00:11:46.949
around, I saw—remember, I told you I

00:11:46.959 --> 00:11:48.790
saw, this would be sensitive to talk

00:11:48.800 --> 00:11:53.030
about, but I saw out of the Berlin area, I

00:11:53.040 --> 00:11:56.630
saw a swastika coming up out of the sky

00:11:56.640 --> 00:12:00.069
that looked like a Batman signal and it

00:12:00.079 --> 00:12:03.509
started to glow in the air. Well,

00:12:03.519 --> 00:12:06.389
when I was interceding on behalf of

00:12:06.399 --> 00:12:08.550
this, I was like, 'Lord, what is this?

00:12:08.560 --> 00:12:10.550
Why did you show this to me?'He started

00:12:10.560 --> 00:12:13.590
to show me what this represented and

00:12:13.600 --> 00:12:18.069
what is going on. I saw satanic people,

00:12:18.079 --> 00:12:21.269
the occult, that were having satanic

00:12:21.279 --> 00:12:25.350
practices in these areas, summoning

00:12:26.880 --> 00:12:31.670
the old Hitler spirit, that demonic

00:12:31.680 --> 00:12:35.590
spirit that was attached to Hitler.

00:12:35.600 --> 00:12:38.150
They were summoning it by witchcraft.

00:12:38.160 --> 00:12:40.870
And I saw actual human sacrifice that

00:12:40.880 --> 00:12:44.230
was taking place around an altar with a

00:12:44.240 --> 00:12:46.710
big pentagram on it. And the Lord

00:12:46.720 --> 00:12:48.710
showed me these elitist people,

00:12:48.710 --> 00:12:48.720
this

00:12:48.720 --> 00:12:50.470
group of people that were doing these

00:12:50.480 --> 00:12:51.990
practices,

00:12:52.000 --> 00:12:57.430
summoning the

00:12:57.440 --> 00:13:00.470
demonic spirit that was on Hitler to

00:13:00.480 --> 00:13:03.509
come on a new entity

00:13:03.519 --> 00:13:09.990
to rise up war and ethnic cleansing.

00:13:10.000 --> 00:13:14.389
A new wave of anti-Semitism

00:13:14.399 --> 00:13:16.790
is coming in a way that we've never seen

00:13:16.800 --> 00:13:18.310
before

00:13:18.320 --> 00:13:20.389
in this generation.

00:13:20.399 --> 00:13:23.350
And as I saw these satanic practices

00:13:23.360 --> 00:13:26.230
taking place when I was praying, I saw

00:13:26.240 --> 00:13:27.910
CERN,

00:13:27.920 --> 00:13:29.829
and there were things that were attached

00:13:29.839 --> 00:13:33.509
to the hydrogen collider and

00:13:33.519 --> 00:13:36.230
CERN. And as they were sending

00:13:36.240 --> 00:13:39.269
up the Batman signal of the swastika, it

00:13:39.279 --> 00:13:42.150
was in the spirit realm. What

00:13:42.160 --> 00:13:44.870
the Batman symbol represented in the

00:13:44.880 --> 00:13:47.750
comic books and what we know is that was

00:13:47.760 --> 00:13:51.030
what brought Batman to that area. It was

00:13:51.040 --> 00:13:55.350
his alert. 'We need that. We need Batman, right?'So

00:13:55.350 --> 00:13:55.360
the

00:13:55.360 --> 00:13:57.509
Batman symbol went up in the

00:13:57.519 --> 00:14:00.389
air. So this was a swastika that went up

00:14:00.399 --> 00:14:02.710
in the air, and it was black, white, and

00:14:02.720 --> 00:14:05.269
red around it, and it went up as a Batman

00:14:05.279 --> 00:14:09.509
symbol over the area of Europe.

00:14:09.519 --> 00:14:11.750
And the Lord showed me that they were

00:14:11.750 --> 00:14:11.760
summoning

00:14:11.760 --> 00:14:15.430
in the spirit a demonic

00:14:15.440 --> 00:14:20.790
wave of a Hitler-type spirit in

00:14:20.790 --> 00:14:20.800
Europe—this

00:14:20.800 --> 00:14:23.670
occult practice.

00:14:23.680 --> 00:14:27.670
As I was praying, I could see

00:14:27.680 --> 00:14:33.269
an uprising of anarchy in France

00:14:33.279 --> 00:14:36.790
like we've not seen before,

